```
Temp: 5 -> cold -> Turn on heater
Temp: 22 -> moderate -> Maintain current settings
Temp: 35 -> hot -> Turn on AC
```

The `classify` node checks thresholds and sets the label. The routing function maps labels to handler names. Each handler sets a specific action. All three handlers connect to `END`.

